name: Stand-Up Meeting
description:
I compose, produce, perform and records my music live in my studio.
I've developed a "metaform" which helps me realize my actual artistic expectations. Electro and techno fit perfectly in this project. I always record in one take. I never save my setup like this, I can't go back to my composition once I've done it. The recording is unique and cannot be redone. New NFTs coming soon.
